<h2 id="local-seo-fundamentals">Local SEO Fundamentals for HVAC Companies</h2>

<div class="prose max-w-none">
<p>Local SEO drives 85% of HVAC leads from search engines. Unlike national SEO, local optimization focuses on geographic relevance and proximity signals that Google uses to determine which businesses appear in the "map pack" results.</p>

<p>The foundation starts with understanding your service area boundaries. HVAC companies serving a 25-mile radius should target neighborhoods, not just the main city. A Phoenix HVAC contractor targeting only "Phoenix AC repair" misses opportunities for "Scottsdale AC repair" or "Tempe HVAC service" where competition might be 60% lower.</p>

<p>Geographic keyword research reveals the most profitable opportunities. Use tools to analyze monthly search volumes and competition levels for each service area combination. Here's what typical search data looks like for a mid-size HVAC company:</p>
