<p>Video content significantly improves engagement metrics that Google considers for rankings. Simple smartphone videos of technicians explaining common issues or showing maintenance tips generate 3x more engagement than text-only content. Upload videos to YouTube with local keywords in titles and descriptions, then embed them on relevant website pages.</p>
