<h2 id="technical-seo-basics">Technical SEO Essentials</h2>

<div class="prose max-w-none">
<p>Technical SEO ensures search engines can crawl, understand, and index your HVAC website effectively. Page speed directly impacts both rankings and conversion rates, with HVAC customers expecting pages to load in under 3 seconds on mobile devices.</p>

<p>Mobile optimization is crucial since 78% of HVAC searches happen on mobile devices. Use Google's Mobile-Friendly Test to identify issues, then prioritize fixes that affect user experience. Ensure phone numbers are clickable, service area maps load quickly, and contact forms work seamlessly on smartphones.</p>

<p>Site structure should reflect your service organization. Create clear URL hierarchies like "/services/ac-repair/phoenix/" that help both users and search engines understand page relationships. Avoid generic URLs like "/page1/" or "/services123/" that provide no context.</p>

<p>SSL certificates and website security affect both rankings and customer trust. HVAC customers entering contact information expect secure connections. Google gives ranking preference to HTTPS sites, and browsers now warn users about unsecured forms on HTTP sites.</p>
</div>

<h2 id="link-building-outreach">Link Building and Outreach</h2>

<div class="prose max-w-none">
<p>Link building for HVAC companies focuses on local relevance and industry authority rather than volume. Ten high-quality local links provide more ranking benefit than 100 low-quality directory submissions.</p>

<p>Local partnership opportunities create natural link-building prospects. Partner with complementary businesses like plumbers, electricians, home security companies, and real estate agents. Offer referral programs that benefit both businesses and create opportunities for mutual linking.</p>

<p>Industry associations and certifications provide valuable link opportunities. Links from ACCA, NATE, or local contractor associations carry significant authority. Maintain active memberships and participate in industry events that generate natural link opportunities.</p>

